constructor.details: Sets the msg.sender as the initial owner via Ownable constructor

params._token: Address of the token to track prices for

latestRoundData().details: This function mimics Chainlink's latestRoundData interface for compatibility with existing integrations

returns._1: answer_ The current price of the token
returns._2: startedAt_ Timestamp when the current round started
returns._3: updatedAt_ Timestamp when the price was last updated
returns._4: answeredInRound_ The round ID in which the answer was computed

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setPrice(uint256).custom:emits: Could emit a PriceUpdated event if implemented
setPrice(uint256).custom:security: Only callable by the contract owner
setPrice(uint256).details: Sets all round data including roundId, price, timestamps, and answeredInRound.      Currently sets roundId to 1 on every update, which could be improved to increment.

params._price: The new price to set, denominated in the precision of the decimals variable

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

answeredInRound().notice: Round ID in which the answer was computed

constructor.notice: Initializes the price feed with the specified token address

decimals().notice: Number of decimal places for the price

latestRoundData().notice: Returns the latest round data in Chainlink AggregatorV3Interface format

roundId().notice: Current round ID for the price feed

setPrice(uint256).notice: Updates the token price to a new value

startedAt().notice: Timestamp when the current round started

token().notice: Address of the token this price feed tracks

updatedAt().notice: Timestamp when the price was last updated
